  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Hotel au Coeur du Village is offered on a half board basis, this includes breakfast and an evening meal. Drinks are not included. </p>
<p>Fuel up for a day skiing at the extensive breakfast buffet which has a variety of sweet and savoury options. Choose from a variety of pastries, yogurts, brioches, fresh fruit or cold cuts, fresh bread and eggs. Additional hot options are also available during breakfast which may have an additional charge. </p>
<p>Half board meals will be taken at the 'Le Coeur' restaurant - a charming and modern mountain restaurant. <span>Each evening you can enjoy a three</span> course <span>à</span> la carte evening meal with choice of menu and daily specials (there is an additional charge for certain dishes). The menu is created around local and fresh products, and the chefs pride themselves on the gourmet offering including a starter, main and dessert.</p>
<p>'Le Cinq' is a cosy and gourmet restaurant which allows you to taste seasonal and traditional dishes which are influenced by international flavours. The restaurant is only open throughout the winter season. Reserve your table locally, additional charges apply.</p>
<div>
<div>Christmas and New Years galas are included. </div>
<span><br /></span>Earlier meal times for children are available from 7pm with a designated children's menu.</div>]]></cateringDescription>
